SYNOPSIS

      # net-mqtt-sub /topic
    
      # net-mqtt-pub /topic message
    
      # net-mqtt-trace mqtt.tcp

DESCRIPTION

    Low level API for the MQTT protocol described at http://mqtt.org.

    IMPORTANT: This is an early release and the API is still subject to
    change.

DISCLAIMER

    This is not official IBM code. I work for IBM but I'm writing this in
    my spare time (with permission) for fun.

SEE ALSO

    net-mqtt-sub(1), net-mqtt-pub(1), net-mqtt-trace(1),
    Net::MQTT::Message(3)

